name: ChemDraw Ultra
description: To access ChemBioOffice (including ChemDraw), register with Cambridgesoft using your NYU/Poly email address here: https://www.cambridgesoft.com/login/ To download the software, log in to your registered account, then click 'My Site Subscription'. To activate the software, use the codes located in the 'My Downloads' section of your account.
